# Design & Naming Rules

## Design
- **Theme:** Dark only. Base background `#070c18`. No white or light backgrounds.
- **Fonts:** Chakra Petch (headings), DM Sans (body), IBM Plex Mono (mono/metadata). Use CSS vars: `--font-chakra`, `--font-dm-sans`, `--font-ibm-mono`. Never use Inter, Roboto, Arial, or system fonts.
- **Colours:** Only CSS variable tokens (e.g. `var(--background)`, `var(--muted-foreground)`). No raw hex in components or pages.
- **Icons:** Stroke width always `1.5` (e.g. Lucide `strokeWidth={1.5}`). Never default 2.
- **Motion:** No looping animations, parallax, or autoplay video (unless muted). Hover 150ms, dropdowns/menus 200ms, section reveals 300–400ms.
- **CTAs:** One primary CTA per section maximum.
- **Cards:** 3px left-border accents only. No full coloured card backgrounds.
- **Body copy:** Max column width 680px.

## Components
- Client components: `"use client"` at top.
- Framer Motion: define variants outside the component, not inline.
- No magic numbers — use spacing and colour tokens only.
- Mobile-first: base styles for mobile, enhance at `lg` breakpoint.

